[Episode 7]

3
00:00:55,050 --> 00:00:59,230
♫Stars hanging in the night sky♫

4
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,560
Your Majesty is also well-versed
in the classics.

5
00:01:01,790 --> 00:01:06,160
♫and sometimes sparkle in the dark♫

6
00:01:02,590 --> 00:01:03,660
don't you know that such matters

7
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:04,870
require mutual affection?

8
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:09,200
Are we not?

9
00:01:08,490 --> 00:01:10,530
♫The wind is blowing♫

10
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:11,960
Answer me.

11
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:13,820
♫The old dream is hidden in my eyes♫

12
00:01:14,890 --> 00:01:15,980
Well...

13
00:01:15,820 --> 00:01:20,800
♫Time passes, but the thousand sorrows remain unresolved♫

14
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,350
We're not.

15
