♫Is it true♫

16
00:01:23,539 --> 00:01:26,350
♫if I get through today, there will be countless days ahead♫

17
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:29,820
♫Trekking thousands of miles, there's still no end♫

18
00:01:29,420 --> 00:01:30,100
Your Majesty.

19
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:36,240
♫All these countless feelings, yet we can't grow old together♫

20
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,680
♫Is it true♫

21
00:01:38,340 --> 00:01:40,910
♫that the past is always in my mind♫

22
00:01:41,979 --> 00:01:44,570
♫It's no different from walking against the water♫

23
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:50,430
♫No matter how many days I count, we still can't be together♫

24
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,259
How come it's you?

25
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:55,080
♫I've been thinking about the past, how can I let it go?♫

26
00:01:53,890 --> 00:01:55,270
Come with me, Shao.

27
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:56,270
I won't go.

28
00:01:55,970 --> 00:01:59,000
♫I love you after all the hardships♫

29
00:01:56,870 --> 00:01:59,350
I know you don't want to marry
my father at all.

30
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:02,670
♫The journey you chose, I was was forced to accept♫

31
00:02:00,540 --> 00:02:01,550
You're wrong.

32
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,420
I want to marry him.

33
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:07,710
♫I take in all the longing and sorrow, how can I just let it go?♫

34
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:08,970
I wanna be the most noble woman
in the world.

35
00:02:08,539 --> 00:02:14,080
♫Longing is like a lump in my throat, a waiting that comes naturally♫

36
00:02:09,289 --> 00:02:10,870
He has so many consorts.

37
00:02:11,070 --> 00:02:11,990
What about you?

38
00:02:12,020 --> 00:02:12,980
So what?

39
00:02:14,260 --> 00:02:16,079
As long as I bear a royal heir,

40
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:20,450
♫It will continue because of you♫

41
00:02:17,990 --> 00:02:20,300
I will have support in this palace.

42
00:02:21,210 --> 00:02:22,540
I can give you

43
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,140
exactly the same thing.

44
00:02:27,060 --> 00:02:28,190
Li Dun!

45
00:02:28,650 --> 00:02:30,230
I said we have no future together.

46
00:02:30,260 --> 00:02:31,900
Don't you understand?

47
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:37,410
What's the point of marrying you?

48
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,260
♫Is it true♫

49
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:39,360
♫if I get through today, there will be countless days ahead♫

50
00:02:38,180 --> 00:02:40,300
You're the least favored among the princes.

51
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:43,100
♫Trekking thousands of miles, there's still no end♫

52
00:02:41,300 --> 00:02:43,140
After His Majesty passes away,

53
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,660
you won't be the new emperor anyway.

54
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:49,520
♫All these countless feelings, yet we can't grow old together♫

55
00:02:47,530 --> 00:02:49,930
The emperor has arrived.

56
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,720
Get up now!

57
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:50,960
♫Is it true♫

58
00:02:51,620 --> 00:02:54,190
♫that the past is always in my mind♫

59
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,700
♫It's no different from walking against the water♫

60
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:58,329
If you truly married my father
for power and status,

61
00:02:58,510 --> 00:03:00,340
you wouldn't be pushing me away now.

62
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:03,710
♫No matter how many days I count, we still can't be together♫

63
00:03:01,320 --> 00:03:04,300
Shao, why did you betray me
in the first place?

64
00:03:04,410 --> 00:03:07,450
[Chengqian Palace]

65
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:08,050
♫I've been thinking about the past, how can I let it go?♫

66
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:12,280
♫I love you after all the hardships♫

67
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,950
♫The journey you chose, I was was forced to accept♫

68
00:03:14,350 --> 00:03:16,630
He truly has feelings for Wen Zhao.

69
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:20,730
♫I take in all the longing and sorrow, how can I just let it go?♫

70
00:03:17,650 --> 00:03:18,790
Perhaps,

71
00:03:19,130 --> 00:03:20,550
I shouldn't linger anymore.

72
00:03:21,820 --> 00:03:27,360
♫Longing is like a lump in my throat, a waiting that comes naturally♫

73
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:30,550
Perhaps I'm not in your heart.

74
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:33,730
♫It will continue because of you♫

75
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:40,790
Your Majesty,

76
00:03:40,820 --> 00:03:44,180
the lack of heirs in the harem is a matter of
national concern.

77
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:48,310
Your Majesty,

78
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:49,460
I have a daughter

79
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,960
who is the younger sister of the Noble Consort.

80
00:03:51,490 --> 00:03:52,850
Her name is Wen Jia.

81
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,829
She is beautiful, well-educated,
and of good character.

82
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:58,120
She is willing to serve Your Majesty
and share your burdens.

83
00:04:07,270 --> 00:04:09,270
The third lady of the Wen family
is indeed beautiful,

84
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:10,730
but she lacks intelligence and spirit.

85
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:13,230
The Empress Dowager could
easily control her.

86
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:15,900
Did Father send Jia here

87
00:04:16,029 --> 00:04:17,700
because he thinks Zhao

88
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,760
is unfit for great use

89
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,240
and wants Jia to replace her?

90
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:22,510
Well.

91
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,310
I need to deal with the Lv family
as soon as possible.

92
00:04:27,220 --> 00:04:27,820
Shao.

93
00:04:28,420 --> 00:04:30,260
How did His Majesty allow you
to leave the palace?

94
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:33,330
Brother.

95
00:04:34,110 --> 00:04:34,909
What's wrong?

96
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:40,230
The cook has gone back to his hometown.

97
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,540
Is the food not to your liking?

98
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:45,380
No. Your cooking

99
00:04:45,409 --> 00:04:47,570
is even better than the imperial chefs
in the palace.

100
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:49,190
It's just that...

101
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,960
I've just recovered from a serious illness,

102
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,750
the smell of these meat

103
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,230
makes me sick.

104
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,980
It's all my fault, it's all my fault.

105
00:04:59,100 --> 00:05:00,680
I should have thought of this.

106
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:02,880
I'll make some lighter dishes
for you next time.

107
00:05:04,650 --> 00:05:06,740
You work hard training all day.

108
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,680
Come,

109
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,490
have more.

110
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,080
Okay.

111
00:05:21,580 --> 00:05:22,570
Brother,

112
00:05:23,130 --> 00:05:25,360
why doesn't His Majesty allow you
to attend court?

113
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:27,360
Is the tiger tally...

114
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:30,790
Don't worry, Shao.

115
00:05:31,210 --> 00:05:32,610
I still have the tiger tally.

116
00:05:36,090 --> 00:05:37,040
Brother,

117
00:05:37,090 --> 00:05:39,050
His Majesty is suspicious of you.

118
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:41,190
Why don't you let me keep
the tiger tally for now?

119
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:42,409
What do you think?

120
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:45,300
Let's eat first.

121
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:55,310
[Hehuan Palace]

122
00:05:54,130 --> 00:05:55,600
Day after day,

123
00:05:55,770 --> 00:05:57,130
I can't get a moment of peace.

124
00:05:57,690 --> 00:05:58,450
Your Majesty.

125
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,280
My dear, look.

126
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,480
These are the memorials sent
by Minister Wen.

127
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,120
Take a look.

128
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:10,970
[I respectfully request Your Majesty to bestow the title of consort upon Wen Jia, to soothe the late emperor's regrets and bless the nation.]

129
00:06:15,110 --> 00:06:17,910
Father wants to offer my sister to
Your Majesty as a consort.

130
00:06:17,980 --> 00:06:20,850
Indeed. He sent seven memorials
for this purpose.

131
00:06:22,290 --> 00:06:24,110
It must be my recent words and actions

132
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,320
that made Minister Wen think
I'm not up to the task,

133
00:06:26,690 --> 00:06:29,270
so he's eager to send another daughter
into the palace to replace me.

134
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,680
What do you think, my love?

135
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,310
What do I think?

136
00:06:34,710 --> 00:06:36,320
I think it's quite good, Your Majesty.

137
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,640
Of course, we must consider taking in a new consort.

138
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:39,560
It's up to Your Majesty's wishes.

139
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,640
I have heard

140
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:48,380
that the third sister of the Wen family

141
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:50,510
is exceptionally beautiful

142
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,940
and virtuous.

143
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:53,770
Why don't we

144
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,470
make her a Noble Consort, just like you?

145
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:03,040
Then I shall thank Your Majesty on behalf
of my sister.

146
00:07:05,690 --> 00:07:06,330
Very well.

147
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:08,500
Since you're so generous,

148
00:07:10,340 --> 00:07:12,620
I shall draft the decree now.

149
00:07:15,130 --> 00:07:16,250
Please proceed, Your Majesty.

150
00:07:18,460 --> 00:07:19,180
A'Bu,

151
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,500
bring me paper and ink.

152
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,360
Yes, Your Majesty.

153
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,340
A'Bu!

154
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:31,790
Go.

155
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:33,730
Don't keep His Majesty waiting.

156
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,080
A'Bu, hurry up!

157
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,350
If you go, you're as good as dead.

158
00:07:42,370 --> 00:07:42,810
Go on.

159
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,360
I...

160
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:45,190
Don't ruin His Majesty's plans.

161
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,620
A'Bu, go quickly!

162
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,000
Don't go.

163
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,720
Should I go or not?

164
00:07:53,770 --> 00:07:55,640
Your Majesty, Noble Consort,

165
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:56,880
should I go or not?

166
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,240
Please give me a clear answer.

167
00:07:58,320 --> 00:07:58,920
Go!

168
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,790
Don't go!

169
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:34,309
[Shoukang Palace]

170
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:41,200
Brother has been away fighting for years,

171
00:08:41,220 --> 00:08:42,760
you must have seen and learned a lot.

172
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,440
I wonder if you could

173
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:45,420
help me find some

174
00:08:45,450 --> 00:08:47,050
poisons that can't be found in Nanming.

175
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,450
What kind of poison do you want?

176
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:53,420
Something lethal

177
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:56,190
but can't be detected as poison.

178
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,140
Are you serious?

179
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,200
Yes, I am.

180
00:09:03,970 --> 00:09:05,450
You want to use it against Wen Zhao?

181
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:08,300
It's for self-protection.

182
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:13,130
Shao, you used to be so kind-hearted.

183
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,810
You would never harm anyone.

184
00:09:15,530 --> 00:09:17,290
But Zhao is constantly trying to harm me.

185
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,240
Can't I fight back?

186
00:09:23,570 --> 00:09:24,690
Brother.

187
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,600
Brother,

188
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:37,420
please help me.

189
00:09:41,050 --> 00:09:42,370
Will you help me or not?

190
00:09:53,790 --> 00:09:54,840
Thank you, Brother.

191
00:10:16,530 --> 00:10:18,510
Princess Jia has arrived.

192
00:10:20,410 --> 00:10:22,390
I heard that Noble Consort Wen
is with child.

193
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:24,370
I specially ordered a bowl of medicine
to be prepared

194
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,280
for your pregnancy.

195
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,090
The Empress Dowager sent you here.

196
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,320
How did you know?

197
00:10:33,110 --> 00:10:35,620
Don't let yourself be used as
a pawn every day.

198
00:10:35,810 --> 00:10:37,290
You've just been released from confinement.

199
00:10:37,770 --> 00:10:39,210
You should be more careful.

200
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:41,280
You're calling me stupid.

201
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,320
Don't want to hear the truth?

202
00:10:43,580 --> 00:10:44,230
Wen Zhao!

203
00:10:48,470 --> 00:10:50,940
Some servants have reported that you
practice black magic,

204
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,300
cursing the Empress Dowager.

205
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,470
Do you admit it?

206
00:10:54,050 --> 00:10:55,770
I advise you to leave immediately.

207
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:57,370
In the harem,

208
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:59,000
you are no match for me.

209
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:00,620
Whether I'm your match or not,

210
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:01,870
we'll know after a search.

211
00:11:01,890 --> 00:11:02,830
Guards!

212
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,260
She doesn't remember it.

213
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:11,160
Search the palace thoroughly.

214
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,690
Help her recall and

215
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:15,290
See if she's done anything
she shouldn't have.

216
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,690
Princess Jia.

217
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:20,620
What right do you have to search my palace?

218
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:22,830
She doesn't have the right.

219
00:11:25,530 --> 00:11:27,250
But I do, don't I?
